WEBINAR Predictions in an Evolving Healthcare Landscape Tuesday, February 14
1 p.m. Eastern Hear fresh perspectives on what health insurance providers can expect in 2023 and the important role integrated virtual care can play. Join us <[[https://www.ahip.org/webinars/predictions-in-an-evolving-health-care-landscape-and-the-significance-of-virtual-care?utm_source=marketo&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=ahipwebinar1_lg&utm_content=registration]]> to hear from our experts on topics including: - Trends that are driving strategic healthcare decisions - Data-driven examples of why and where these decisions take place - Preparing for rapidly shifting market needs Hear from our event speakers: Matt Eyles President & CEO AHIP Kelly Bliss President of U.S. Group Health Teladoc Health About Teladoc Health: Teladoc Health is transforming the healthcare experience and empowering people everywhere to live healthier lives. Recognized as the world leader in whole-person virtual care, Teladoc Health leverages more than a decade of expertise and data-driven insights to meet the growing virtual care needs of consumers and healthcare professionals.
